|cblueFight Type:|r 

{tank} Stack & swap when debuff expires
{tank} Position boss away from center of room
{tank} Keep Flame add 15 yards  away from other adds
{dps}+{healer} Spread out, stack behind boss at 100 energy

|corange--- 100 Energy ---
Raid stack behind boss
{tank} Use a CD to solo soak the first hit, then turn towards the raid
{tank} 2nd tank taunt and do the same

|corange--- Intermission ---
Keep Embers away from boss (All CC works on these)
Kill Flame add to end intermission phase

|credHeroic:
Adds don't despawn after intermission: Let 1 hit the boss every 15 seconds
Don't kill Flame add until all Embers are gone